---
description: BoonBuy AI and product catalog safety rules
globs:
  - src/lib/ai/**
  - src/components/ai/**
  - src/app/api/ai/**
  - src/app/ai/**
---

- Preserve the current website design and branding.
- Never invent product records, prices, URLs, ratings, or stock.
- Reuse existing ProductCard / ProductGrid / affiliate helpers.
- Use strict TypeScript; validate API input with Zod.
- Keep provider API keys server-side only.
- Do not silently alter affiliate URLs or invite codes.
- Prefer modular, reviewable changes over broad refactors.
- Maintain mobile responsiveness and accessibility for AI UI.
